data.description: Move in ready bungalow located near downtown Bristol. Crisply updated with great attention to detail. Everything you want is located on the main level, bedroom, office, kitchen, full bathroom, and laundry. Additionally, there are two bedrooms on the second floor with an additional bedroom featuring its own bath and spacious walk-in closet with an adjoining den situated downstairs, with a walk out. There is also ample storage space in the oversized utility/storage room. This home is nestled on an oversized lot with plenty of space in the rear of the home for the kiddos and your favorite fur babies. No worries on the appliances, windows, heat pump, or roof. All newer if not brand new as well.
